room_title: Escape room "Serum 42" by Moore Escape Rooms in Oklahoma City
room_description:
All Agents,
An individual codenamed "Dr. Evil" has completed his ferocious mutating serum and is about to unleash it on the world! In order for us to create the antidote, you must infiltrate his laboratory and find the recipe within an hour.
Are you willing to accept this mission?
